  <brief_title>Study to Explore the Mechanism of Acquired Immune Escape In Participants With Metastatic Cancer Progressing on CPI Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter Study to Explore the Mechanism of Acquired Immune Escape In Patients With Metastatic Cancer Progressing on Checkpoint Inhibitor Therapy</official_title>
